<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<title>COSY</title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
		<link
			rel="preload"
			href="https://{{jitsiDomain}}/external_api.js"
			as="script"
		/>
		<link rel="preload" href="/js/app.js" as="script" />
		<style>
			.svg-pan-zoom-control {
				cursor: pointer !important;
				fill: white !important;
				fill-opacity: 1 !important;
			}
			.svg-pan-zoom-control:hover {
				fill-opacity: 1 !important;
			}
			.svg-pan-zoom-control-background {
				fill: black !important;
			}
			.svg-pan-zoom-control-background {
				fill-opacity: 1 !important;
			}
			#graphic-settings-content {
				display: none;
			}
			#graphic-settings:target #graphic-settings-content {
				display: inline-block;
			}
			#graphic-settings:target #open-graphic-settings {
				display: none;
			}
		</style>
		<script>
			window.synyxoffice = {
				jitsiDomain: "{{jitsiDomain}}",
				player: {
					name: "{{player.name}}",
					email: "{{player.email}}",
					avatarUrl: "{{player.avatarUrl}}",
				},
			};
		</script>
	</head>
	<body class="bg-grey">
		{{> chat}}
		{{> arcade}}
		<ul
			id="action-menu"
			class="hidden fixed z-40 text-black text-xs shadow-outline font-bold font-mono bg-white opacity-75 border border-black rounded"
		></ul>
		<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 p-4 z-10">
		</div>
		<div class="absolute top-0 p-4" style="max-width: 40%; max-height: 40%">
			<ul>
				<li class="mb-2">
					&raquo; Du kannst Dich mit den Pfeiltasten auf deiner Tastatur fortbewegen.
				</li>
				<li class="mb-2">
					&raquo; Halte Shift gedrückt, um dich schneller bewegen zu können.
				</li>
				<li class="mb-2">
					&raquo; Klicke auf deinen Avatar, um ein Gespräch zu starten oder eines der versteckten Features zu entdecken.
				</li>
				<li class="mb-2">
					&raquo; Wenn ein Nutzer ein Gespräch gestartet hat, siehst Du einen grünen Kreis um ihn. Gehe in seine Nähe und tritt dem Video-Call bei.
				</li>
				<li class="mb-2">
					&raquo; Findest du die Kaffeemaschinen? Geh doch mal hin und klicke auf deinen Avatar.
				</li>
				<li class="mb-2">
					&raquo; Seid nett zueinander.
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 z-10 flex flex-col items-end">
			<div class="mb-4">
					Name: {{name}}
			</div>
			<div class="mb-4">
				<form id="logout-form" action="/logout" method="POST">
					<input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="{{{csrf}}}" />
					<button
									type="submit"
									class="border bg-white text-black font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded-sm"
					>
						Feierabend
					</button>
				</form>
			</div>
			<div id="graphic-settings"
					 class="mt-4">
				<a href="#graphic-settings"
					 id="open-graphic-settings"
					 class="border bg-white text-black font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded-sm">Graphic settings</a>
				<div id="graphic-settings-content"
						 class="border bg-white text-black py-2 px-4 rounded-sm">
					<p>Wenn die Seite ruckelt, kannst Du hier Gegenstände ausblenden:</p>
					<ul class="mb-2">
						<li>
							<label>
								<input
												id="show-desks-office"
												type="checkbox"
												checked="checked"
								/>&nbsp;
								<span>Großraum</span>
							</label>
						</li>
						<li>
							<label>
								<input
												id="show-desks-10vorne"
												type="checkbox"
												checked="checked"
								/>&nbsp;
								<span>10vorne</span>
							</label>
						</li>
						<li>
							<label>
								<input id="show-wasser" type="checkbox" checked="checked" />&nbsp;
								<span>Wasser</span>
							</label>
						</li>
						<li>
							<label>
								<input
												id="show-nullpointer"
												type="checkbox"
												checked="checked"
								/>&nbsp;
								<span>Nullpointer</span>
							</label>
						</li>
						<li>
							<label>
								<input id="show-kueche" type="checkbox" checked="checked" />&nbsp;
								<span>Küche</span>
							</label>
						</li>
						<li>
							<label>
								<input id="show-balkon" type="checkbox" checked="checked" />&nbsp;
								<span>Balkon</span>
							</label>
						</li>
						<li>
							<label>
								<input
												id="show-wohnzimmer"
												type="checkbox"
												checked="checked"
								/>&nbsp;
								<span>Wohnzimmer</span>
							</label>
						</li>
						<li>
							<label>
								<input id="show-kreativ" type="checkbox" checked="checked" />&nbsp;
								<span>Kreativraum</span>
							</label>
						</li>
						<li>
							<label>
								<input id="show-memory" type="checkbox" checked="checked" />&nbsp;
								<span>Memory-Leak</span>
							</label>
						</li>
						<li>
							<label>
								<input id="show-billard" type="checkbox" checked="checked" />&nbsp;
								<span>Billard</span>
							</label>
						</li>
						<li>
							<label>
								<input
												id="show-office-maedels"
												type="checkbox"
												checked="checked"
								/>&nbsp;
								<span>Office</span>
							</label>
						</li>
						<li>
							<label>
								<input id="show-plants" type="checkbox" checked="checked" />&nbsp;
								<span>Pflanzen</span>
							</label>
						</li>
						<li>
							<label>
								<input id="show-bins" type="checkbox" checked="checked" />&nbsp;
								<span>Mülleimer</span>
							</label>
						</li>
						<li>
							<label>
								<input
												id="show-cupboards"
												type="checkbox"
												checked="checked"
								/>&nbsp;
								<span>Regale</span>
							</label>
						</li>
						<li>
							<label>
								<input id="show-boards" type="checkbox" checked="checked" />&nbsp;
								<span>Boards</span>
							</label>
						</li>
					</ul>
					<a href="#hide-graphic-settings"
						 id="close-graphic-settings"
						 class="border bg-white text-black font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded-sm mb-2">Close</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="w-screen h-screen relative">
			{{> office}}
		</div>
		<script async src="https://{{jitsiDomain}}/external_api.js"></script>
		<script
			async
			type="module"
			crossorigin="use-credentials"
			src="/js/app.js"
		></script>
		{{> application-version-info-script}}
	</body>
</html>
